metadata.name: Genius of Solitude
metadata.description:
The genius of solitude
Is the one that I choose
I love my own company
And I can never lose

When I'm all by myself
I am in control
My mind is at ease
My heart is full

The beauty of being alone
Is that I know what I'm looking for
My inner wisdom is strong
And I'm not settling for more

The genius of solitude
Is the only way to go
It's the path to enlightenment
And the best way to know

The power of being alone
Is the ultimate source of strength
I'm not searching for approval
But instead a peace within myself
